wee
Homonym Number:
Word Class:adjective
Sense Number:
Definition:little (originally esp. in Otago and Southland, but now general)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: shared with and deriving from Scots English
